## Cor 8.19 bridge: Thaine route (post 2026-05-06 expert review)

The `Cor8_19Bridge 37 K_37 32` field is now discharged via Thaine's
annihilator theorem, not via Sinnott's regulator computation. Reviewer
recommendation: split the bridge into the four-field decomposition

```
FLT37UnitClassBridge 37 K_37 32
  ├── pollaczekUnitComponent : realLocalCert ⟹ (E⁺/C⁺)(ω^32, 37) trivial
  ├── thaineComponent : (E⁺/C⁺)(ω^32, 37) trivial ⟹ Cl(K⁺)(ω^32, 37) trivial
