  │ Cl(K⁺)(ω^j, 37) trivial (via Spiegelungssatz + Herbrand–Ribet)
  └── hPlusOfComponents : ∀ j, Cl(K⁺)(ω^j, 37) trivial ⟹ ¬ 37 ∣ hPlus K
```

then chain via `cor8_19Bridge_of_unitClassBridge` (in
`PlusCoprime/Thaine/UnitClassBridge.lean`). The Thaine annihilator at
single character `ω^32` (the substantive remaining piece) avoids both the
Sinnott regulator determinant and the Iwasawa Main Conjecture; see
[Wash97 2nd ed §15] (Thaine/Kolyvagin/Rubin chapters), [Rubin00] *Euler
Systems*, and Kučera (single-character corollary). Foundational Sinnott
identities shipped earlier (full→half log-sin sum, χ-substitution,
matrix-eigenvalue, second-kind orthogonality) remain in
`PlusCoprime/Sinnott/{Determinant,AnalyticProof}.lean` as reusable library
lemmas — correct mathematics, no longer on the critical path.

